title: PsySutra - Air Trance Corporation (Red Sun Rising Remix)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

After the release of his debut album 'Gamma Phoenicis' on Cronomi Records, back in summer of 2014, one of the most creative Goa trance producers from Poland - Łukasz Wiącek returns with his PsySutra project and new 4-track EP 'Nebulla Cebulla' on Neogoa Records.  Download Nebulla Cebulla - http://www.neogoa.net/nebulla-cebulla/

Tracklist:

01 – PsySutra - Infinnitus Anniversarius (146 BPM)
02 – PsySutra - Semper Fi (150 BPM)
03 – Artha - Insidelamp (PsySutra Remix) (136 BPM)
04 – PsySutra - Air Trance Corporation (Red Sun Rising Remix) (114 BPM)
